<plot>A close group of friends are confronted by anger and racism on the basketball court they call home: Astoria Park. For Aman, Taso, and their friends, it would be just another day on the basketball court. Today however, the summer heat would bring familiar enemies with other plans. With basketball and freestyle rap as the platform, each crew struggles to protect its identity and territory in the uncomfortable racial dynamic that is post 9/11 New York City. Tensions rise, and the anger escalates into a high-octane fully charged battle of wits and will.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?049174</url></doc>
